sis of the true horizontal growth\nprocess. This is inspired by works on the long range contact process [Probab.\nTh. Rel. Fields (1995), 102, 519-545]. A renormalization scheme is used for the\npercolative regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 19:23:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2019 09:16:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 15:03:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
