e non-thermal\ncomponent in order to be consistent with optical observations. Motivated by the\ngood quality of the synchrotron fits, we explore the physical parameter space\nof the emitting region. In a basic prompt emission scenario we find quite\ncontrived solutions for the magnetic field strength (5 G $<B^\\prime<40$ G) and\nfor the location of the region where the radiation is produced\n($R_\\gamma>10^{16}$ cm).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 22:08:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 16:04:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
